The paper deals with the problem of private information retrieval (PIR) and symmetric private information retrieval (SPIR) for a distributed database stored using an MDS storage code. This involves concepts from information theory (cs.IT), cryptography (cs.CR), distributed systems (cs.DS), coding theory (cs.CC), and databases (cs.DB). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
